quran[12{c,v,t}:
19,65,woh rab hai asmano ka aur zameen ka aur unn saari cheezon ka jo aasman o zameen ke darmain hain pas tum uss ke bandagi karo aur usi ki bandagi par saabit qadam raho kya hai koi hasti tumahray ilm mein is ki hum paya ?
19,66,ensaan kehta hai kya waqai jab mein mar chukun ga to phir zindah kar ke nikaal laya jaoon ga ?
19,67,kya ensaan ko yaad nahi aata ke hum pehlay is ko peda kar chuke hain jabkay woh kuch bhi nah tha ?
19,68,"tairay Rab ki qasam, hum zaroor un sab ko aur un ke sath shyatin ko bhi ghair layein ge, phir jahannum ke gird laa kar inhen ghutnon ke bil gira den ge"
19,69,phir har giroh mein se har uss shakhs ko chhant len ge jo Rehman ke muqablay mein ziyada sarkash bana howa tha
19,70,phir yeh hum jantay hain ke un mein se kon sab se barh kar jahannum mein jhonkay jaane ka mustahiq hai
19,71,"tum mein se koi aisa nahi hai jo jahannum par warid nah ho, yeh to aik tey shuda baat hai jisay poora karna tairay rab ka zimma hai"
19,72,phir hum unn logon ko bacha len ge jo ( duniya mein ) mut-taqi thay aur zaalmon ko usi mein gira howa chore den ge
19,73,"inn logon ko jab hamari khُli khُli ayaat sunai jati hain to inkaar karne walay imaan laane walon se kehte hain"" batao hum dono garohoon mein se kon behtar haalat mein hai aur kis ki mujlisain ziyada shandaar hain? """
19,74,halaank un se pehlay hum kitni hi aisi qomon ko halaak kar chuke hain jo inn se ziyada sir o samaan rakhti theen aur zahiri shaan o Shaukat mein inn se barhi hui theen
19,75,"inn se kaho, jo shakhs gumraahi mein mubtala hota hai ussay Rehman dheel diya karta hai yahan taq ke jab aisay log woh cheez dekh letay hain jis ka unn se wada kya gaya hai khuwa woh azaab Ellahi ho ya qayamat ki gharri tab inhen maloom ho jata hai ke kis ka haal kharab hai aur kis ka jatha kamzor !"
19,76,is ke bar aks jo log raah e raast ikhtiyar karte hain Allah un ko raast rawi mein taraqqi ataa farmata hai aur baqi reh jaane wali naikian hi tairay rab ke nazdeek jaza aur injaam ke aitbaar se behtar hain
